               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390617-name-825" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-825" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-825" type="surname" value="BROWN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-825" type="given" value="CAROLINE"></interp>CAROLINE BROWN</persName>
                  </hi>. I take care of a house for Mr. James Cummins, at Westminster—the furniture is his—I let beds for the night—the prisoner came there on the 15th of June for a bed—I had not known him before—he was to pay 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—he went to bed, and got up the next morning at half-past eight or a quarter to nine o'clock—I missed the sheets after he was gone—these are them—they were put clean on the bed.</p>
